Parameter.Name: CreateFullRecords
Parameter.Comment: Should be set to true for SSL interface.

Parameter.Name: OpraThirdPartyExpirationDates
Parameter.Comment: Set true to use only third-party expiration dates e.g. from OCC series file, as OPRA does not distinguish the "Quarterly" options from NYSE or ISE from normal options.

Parameter.Name: SleepAtEndOfTransmission
Parameter.Comment: so that test data is ignored

Parameter.Name: LineFilterMinSeqNumberSetInterval
Parameter.Comment: Interval (in seconds) during which any repeated seq number resets are ignored

Parameter.Name: LineFilterMaxValidGapSize
Parameter.Comment: Largest acceptable sequence number gap for incoming data Messages showing gaps exceeding this value will be discarded
This parameter must be set to true for any block format data transmitting using FAST protocol
